WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.242 --> 00:00:11.805
What are your expectations?

00:00:12.232 --> 00:00:14.619
I have great expectations,

00:00:15.625 --> 00:00:21.316
this is a huge Club,
with outstanding fans,

00:00:21.821 --> 00:00:25.134
and I hope I manage
to do what I did back there...

00:00:25.135 --> 00:00:28.652
and even more
to help my teammates...

00:00:28.653 --> 00:00:30.151
during this year.

00:00:30.619 --> 00:00:32.326
You started training,

00:00:32.327 --> 00:00:33.975
you're fitting in,

00:00:33.976 --> 00:00:35.413
what do you think about
our Training Center,

00:00:35.414 --> 00:00:36.517
about your teammates,

00:00:37.015 --> 00:00:38.845
are you happy to be here?

00:00:39.081 --> 00:00:42.222
I'm happy to be here,

00:00:42.484 --> 00:00:46.110
this is one of the best
Training Centers in Brazil,

00:00:46.529 --> 00:00:48.901
everyone welcomed me,

00:00:48.902 --> 00:00:53.674
all my teammates welcomed me,

00:00:53.964 --> 00:00:56.829
and I hope I can play soon
in order to help.

00:00:56.981 --> 00:01:02.299
I'm very happy
we managed to sign Rildo,

00:01:02.846 --> 00:01:07.097
an athlete we've been keeping an eye on
since the Brazilian Championship...

00:01:08.087 --> 00:01:09.761
and the Copa Sudamericana,

00:01:09.762 --> 00:01:14.043
we've been watching him
for a while.

00:01:14.259 --> 00:01:17.952
He had a great season,
other teams were interested in him,

00:01:18.924 --> 00:01:21.584
that's why we took a while
to sign him,

00:01:22.327 --> 00:01:26.395
but I'm really happy
because he wanted to come to Santos,

00:01:27.419 --> 00:01:30.021
and I believe
he'll be very successful here...

00:01:30.799 --> 00:01:33.967
due to everything Santos FC
has to offer to him.

00:01:33.968 --> 00:01:36.513
Our head coach is pleased with
his playing attributes,

00:01:36.514 --> 00:01:39.698
he asked us to sign him.

00:01:40.585 --> 00:01:44.403
He's a very fast and skilled player,

00:01:44.404 --> 00:01:48.800
he has everything needed
to be successful,

00:01:48.801 --> 00:01:50.863
and to make our fans happy,

00:01:50.864 --> 00:01:54.336
he's a great option
to the team we're building,

00:01:54.593 --> 00:01:56.639
it'll be a winning team.

00:01:56.640 --> 00:02:01.603
I'm very happy
we signed him,

00:02:01.824 --> 00:02:05.123
I wish him all the best,

00:02:05.464 --> 00:02:09.669
we'll give him everything he needs
to be happy,

00:02:10.436 --> 00:02:16.072
so that he can do
what he does better,

00:02:16.073 --> 00:02:17.688
which is playing soccer.

00:02:17.806 --> 00:02:20.369
Hello, Santos fans,
this is Rildo,

00:02:20.370 --> 00:02:24.988
I hope to be very successful
during 2014 along with my mates,

00:02:24.989 --> 00:02:27.462
winning several titles.

00:02:41.455 --> 00:02:42.718
I looks great!

